com.betfair.cougar.util.jmx

Interface ExportableRegistration


  • public interface ExportableRegistration
    Interface for registering JMX Exportable classes. The ExportableRegistration implementation should be aware of a JMXControl, and will call export() on all registered Exportables as soon as the JMXControl becomes available.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void registerExportable(Exportable exportable)
      Register an Exportable class, so that it may be exported to JMX as soon as the JMXControl is available.

    • Method Detail

      • registerExportable

        Register an Exportable class, so that it may be exported to JMX as soon as the JMXControl is available.
        Parameters:
        exportable - class that can be exported to JMX
